descriptionHtml:
Welcome to my first mod

This is a simple house with all your crafting needs outside and inside.
With a few extra\'s inside but i dont want to spoil it but you can find it in the basement.

i\'ll try to update this house if possible so any feedback ond/or sugestions will be welcome

enjoy

p.s. you might want to get rid of your neighbour first ;)

Update 1.1

I did a small update to get rid of the noises that came from the basement.
Also I added 4 mannequin, got rid of the weapon rack and placed some rugs in the bedroom and enchanting room i felt like something was missing.
